+        "- `06_RESEARCH/CODE/output/tsmom_dual_S_trades.csv`",
+        "- `06_RESEARCH/CODE/output/tsmom_dual_S_equity.csv`",
+        "- `06_RESEARCH/CODE/output/tsmom_dual_S_metrics.json`",
