+        "| fee each side | 0.0005 in legacy P1-06 code | 0.001 per Protocol v1.3/AGENTS |",
+        f"| slippage each side | 0.001 | {SLIPPAGE_RATE} |",
+        "| funding | real 8H direction-aware | real 8H direction-aware |",
